{
  "title": "pakabariw a saysay no Poli Pazeh a saw",
  "titleCh": "埔里族人的經濟作物",
  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "居住在埔里鄉鎮的巴宰族人，過去的日子，很多人的工作是務農，從前很多農地種植著稻米和紅甘蔗，後來慢慢出現了轉變，變成種植茭白筍（俗稱水筍）了！烏牛欄出的茭白筍品質很好，口感甜美，有好的水，長出來的筍子是又白又嫩，所以埔里的人們都稱讚茭白筍為「美人腿」。",
      "ab": "malalēng di Poli rutul a Pazeh saw ka. okua a dali. sasa saw ukukusa ka umamahan. ohoda ka sasa umamahan ka paxoruma’ēn mulasi iu tubus lubaheng. aubil a dali ka matu’adang lai pakinakaw. maxa paxoruma’ēn ali dalum lia. Auran marukat a ali dalum ka haw riak. tuxubus riak a kakanēn. imini a daxē ka nahada riak a dalum. marukat a si’ali’an ka risilaw iu rabēx huhul lia. maluhosu. Poli a sawsaw maadēkas ali dalum ka “karaw u kiarēn mamais” sēn.",
      "order": "1",
